    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Rootgnaw Grubs are dog-sized insectoid larvae warped by the blight of the Ashen Woods. They burrow through loose soil and ash, erupting in swarms to latch onto prey and gnaw through armour with their corrosive mandibles. Where grubs swarm, their Queen is never far behind.</p>",
      "director": "<p>Rootgnaw Grubs are minions — use them in groups of 4 with a shared Stamina pool. They burrow toward isolated PCs and use Gnaw to latch on, dealing ongoing damage that forces the target to waste actions removing them. Spawn more via the Rootgnaw Queen's Brood-Mother feature. Burrow speed 3 is noted in their description — they can move through loose soil but are slow at it.</p>",
